  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Bust-a-Move DS, known as Hippatte!! Puzzle Bobble (Japanese: ひっぱって!!パズルボブル, Hepburn: Hippatte!! Pazuru Boburu; \"Pull Back!! Puzzle Bobble\") in Japan, is a puzzle video game developed by Happy Happening and published by Majesco Entertainment for the Nintendo DS handheld video game console.\nThe game received mixed reaction due to the game lacking new features apart from the new slingshot system.",
